{"title":"NLP Quick Reference Guide","html":"<h1 id=\"nlp-quick-reference-guide\">NLP Quick Reference Guide</h1>\n<p>Quick reference for NLP techniques, code snippets, and best practices.</p>\n<h2 id=\"table-of-contents\">Table of Contents</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#text-preprocessing\">Text Preprocessing</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#word-embeddings\">Word Embeddings</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#model-architectures\">Model Architectures</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#transformers\">Transformers</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#common-issues-solutions\">Common Issues &amp; Solutions</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#best-practices-checklist\">Best Practices Checklist</a></li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"text-preprocessing\">Text Preprocessing</h2>\n<h3 id=\"basic-pipeline\">Basic Pipeline</h3>\n<pre class=\"shiki dark-plus\" style=\"background-color:#1E1E1E;color:#D4D4D4\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#C586C0\">import</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> re</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#C586C0\">from</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> nltk.tokenize </span><span style=\"color:#C586C0\">import</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> word_tokenize</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#C586C0\">from</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> nltk.corpus </span><span style=\"color:#C586C0\">import</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> stopwords</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#569CD6\">def</span><span style=\"color:#DCDCAA\"> preprocess</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">(</span><span style=\"color:#9CDCFE\">text</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">):</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">    text = text.lower()</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">    text = re.sub(</span><span style=\"color:#569CD6\">r</span><span style=\"color:#D16969\">'</span><span style=\"color:#CE9178\">[^</span><span style=\"color:#D16969\">\\w\\s</span><span style=\"color:#CE9178\">]</span><span style=\"color:#D16969\">'</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">, </span><span style=\"color:#CE9178\">''</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">, text)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">    tokens = word_tokenize(text)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">    tokens = [w </span><span style=\"color:#C586C0\">for</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> w </span><span style=\"color:#C586C0\">in</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> tokens </span><span style=\"color:#C586C0\">if</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> w </span><span style=\"color:#569CD6\">not</span><span style=\"color:#569CD6\"> in</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> stopwords.words(</span><span style=\"color:#CE9178\">'english'</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">)]</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#C586C0\">    return</span><span style=\"color:#CE9178\"> ' '</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">.join(tokens)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span></code></pre>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"word-embeddings\">Word Embeddings</h2>\n<h3 id=\"word2vec\">Word2Vec</h3>\n<pre class=\"shiki dark-plus\" style=\"background-color:#1E1E1E;color:#D4D4D4\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#C586C0\">from</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> gensim.models </span><span style=\"color:#C586C0\">import</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> Word2Vec</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">model = Word2Vec(sentences, </span><span style=\"color:#9CDCFE\">vector_size</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">=</span><span style=\"color:#B5CEA8\">100</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">, </span><span style=\"color:#9CDCFE\">window</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">=</span><span style=\"color:#B5CEA8\">5</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">vector = model.wv[</span><span style=\"color:#CE9178\">'word'</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">]</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"pre-trained-embeddings\">Pre-trained Embeddings</h3>\n<pre class=\"shiki dark-plus\" style=\"background-color:#1E1E1E;color:#D4D4D4\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#6A9955\"># GloVe, FastText, etc.</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#6A9955\"># Use in Keras Embedding layer</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span></code></pre>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"model-architectures\">Model Architectures</h2>\n<h3 id=\"lstm\">LSTM</h3>\n<pre class=\"shiki dark-plus\" style=\"background-color:#1E1E1E;color:#D4D4D4\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">model = keras.Sequential([</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">    layers.Embedding(vocab_size, </span><span style=\"color:#B5CEA8\">128</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">),</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">    layers.LSTM(</span><span style=\"color:#B5CEA8\">64</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">),</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">    layers.Dense(</span><span style=\"color:#B5CEA8\">1</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">, </span><span style=\"color:#9CDCFE\">activation</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">=</span><span style=\"color:#CE9178\">'sigmoid'</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">])</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"transformers\">Transformers</h3>\n<pre class=\"shiki dark-plus\" style=\"background-color:#1E1E1E;color:#D4D4D4\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#C586C0\">from</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> transformers </span><span style=\"color:#C586C0\">import</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> pipeline</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">classifier = pipeline(</span><span style=\"color:#CE9178\">\"sentiment-analysis\"</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span></code></pre>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"common-issues-amp-solutions\">Common Issues &amp; Solutions</h2>\n<h3 id=\"issue-1-out-of-vocabulary\">Issue 1: Out-of-Vocabulary</h3>\n<p><strong>Solution</strong>: Use FastText or BERT subword tokenization</p>\n<h3 id=\"issue-2-long-sequences\">Issue 2: Long Sequences</h3>\n<p><strong>Solution</strong>: Truncate or use models for long sequences</p>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"best-practices-checklist\">Best Practices Checklist</h2>\n<ul>\n<li> Preprocess text properly</li>\n<li> Use appropriate sequence length</li>\n<li> Try pre-trained embeddings</li>\n<li> Use transformers for best results</li>\n<li> Handle variable-length sequences</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Try next:</strong> Transformers are state-of-the-art - use them!</p>\n","source":"12-natural-language-processing/nlp-quick-reference.md","githubUrl":"https://github.com/NabidAlam/road-to-machine-learning/blob/main/12-natural-language-processing/nlp-quick-reference.md","module":"12-natural-language-processing","lessonId":"nlp-quick-reference","guideId":null,"type":"module","readingMinutes":1}